r #KrishnaNaam #VrindavanChandrodayaMandir"},"code":"DZcolOdyUUV","display_uri":"https:\/\/scontent.cdninstagram.com\/v\/t51.82787-15\/722131885_18569048554064801_2474077998619772172_n.webp?stp=dst-jpg_e35_s640x640_tt6&_nc_cat=109&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiRkVFRC5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=uKEKD-dbwXgQ7kNvwHzYNUr&_nc_oc=Adpyq7qaH3BwKO3C-gDWtEBKN9RGfgavVuUKHv0i627shSlPq3gxun-JBC8oSfpHcuVbWtopHZOIkyNbIZkpKeuS&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent.cdninstagram.com&_nc_gid=fcdkUnviKqhXyl67TmBjxA&_nc_ss=78289&oh=00_Af8a5PLKkFlL57VtY64OFfEY_rwgI17DXL_YrfhmHEFZcQ&oe=6A33104B","media_type":1,"product_type":"feed","user":{"pk":"1921864800","username":"vcmvrindavan","id":"17841401944000233"},"id":"POLARIS_3917184255918687509"}},{"node":{"__typename":"XIGPolarisCarouselMedia","pk":"3917156665381241317","__isXIGPolarisMedia":"XIGPolarisCarouselMedia","accessibility_caption":"Photo by Vrindavan Chandrodaya Mandir on June 11, 2026.","caption":{"text":"By the blessings of our presiding Deities, Sri Radha Vrindavanchandra, Sri Nitai Gauranga and our Spiritual Master, Vishwaguru Srila Prabhupada, the ongoing Vrindavan Chandrodaya Mandir project is witnessing noteworthy developments, reflecting the scale, dedication, and craftsmanship invested in every phase of construction.\n\nHere is a throwback of the developments over the last few years in pictures."},"code":"DZciTuxmkHl","display_uri":"https:\/\/scontent.cdninstagram.com\/v\/t51.82787-15\/721779220_18569036524064801_7573181753057844538_n.heic?stp=dst-jpg_e35_s640x640_tt6&_nc_cat=107&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0FST1VTRUxfSVRFTS5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=97T1uzdJ84AQ7kNvwFRqTcD&_nc_oc=Adpr8N6ZWoDjCv4LStYrPiO7d-dULAQc7toM3VDcdaLCeAo6bFUsN3ifCVkF81aVAipx5iTie8uxJAU8m8JbaMms&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent.cdninstagram.com&_nc_gid=fcdkUnviKqhXyl67TmBjxA&_nc_ss=78289&oh=00_Af8BHdUCcqnrx6vDfyYilO0LRxxkVUI6AK9YHU8Nsuic0Q&oe=6A331555","media_type":8,"product_type":"carousel_container","user":{"pk":"1921864800","username":"vcmvrindavan","id":"17841401944000233"},"carousel_media_count":6,"id":"POLARIS_3917156665381241317"}},{"node":{"__typename":"XIGPolarisVideoMedia","pk":"3917057807551597202","__isXIGPolarisMedia":"XIGPolarisVideoMedia","accessibility_caption":"Video by Vrindavan Chandrodaya Mandir on June 11, 2026. May be an image of poster, concert and text that says 'MUSC MM ACIEMANDS MANDS Vrindavan Chandrodaya Chanaro Chandr odaya Mandir Title ESP Buildpro dpro Buik \u1021\u101e\u101b\u1030\u1001\u103a\u1001\u102b 14TH JUNE 2026 WHITE FEATHER CONVENTION, BANGALORE TICKETS AVAILABLE ON allevents district FR book my show VCM Official Website LIMITED TICKETS AVAILABLE'.","caption":{"text":"Bangalore, get ready for the biggest Bhakti Jamming Concert of the year! \ud83c\udfb6\n\nAn unforgettable evening with Maithili Thakur, where devotion meets music and thousands of voices unite in the holy names of Radha Krishna. \ud83d\ude4f\n\nLose yourself in soulful bhajans, powerful kirtans, and an atmosphere filled with divine energy.\n\n\ud83d\udccd White Feather Convention, Bangalore\n\ud83d\udcc5 14th June 2026\n\nCome for the music. Stay for the bhakti. Leave with a transformed heart.\n\n#BhaktiJammingConcert #MaithiliThakur #MusicForMandir #KrishnaBhakti #VrindavanChandrodayaMandir"},"code":"DZcL1KPyIqS","display_uri":"https:\/\/scontent.cdninstagram.com\/v\/t51.71878-15\/720647274_1487223379132242_6580720979904151302_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_s640x640_tt6&_nc_cat=102&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0xJUFMuYmVzdF9pbWFnZV91cmxnZW4uQzMifQ\u00253D\u00253D&_nc_ohc=kRSOSNzHLdwQ7kNvwF-zBJ4&_nc_oc=AdrYoRKB_Z_OE7AKi3wEfTN4Cq_Oo9JiHvVjid2SllrZBwCMbPddPL3IWoRqiRKTtEXX3YWwutX8HOwYffZn2v8e&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent.cdninstagram.com&_nc_gid=fcdkUnviKqhXyl67TmBjxA&_nc_ss=78289&oh=00_Af-I950meZx_5UA8vm210bruq3JnX1m7Ihoy8U1IeBiUKw&oe=6A32F00B","media_type":2,"product_type":"clips","user":{"pk":"1921864800","username":"vcmvrindavan","id":"17841401944000233"},"id":"POLARIS_3917057807551597202"}},{"node":{"__typename":"XIGPolarisVideoMedia","pk":"3916987564829451271","__isXIGPolarisMedia":"XIGPolarisVideoMedia","accessibility_caption":"Video by Vrindavan Chandrodaya Mandir on June 11, 2026. May be an image of lighting, crowd, outdoors, night and text that says 'Vrindavan Chandrodaya Mandir \u039fO\u039f\u0424\u039d\u03a5\u0391 RISINGMOONOF VRINDAVAN MUSICrONMANDIR MUSIC MANDIR Ano 5\u0e07'.","caption":{"text":"Ahmedabad immersed itself in the magic of the Maha Mantra. \u2728\u2764\ufe0f\n\nThousands of voices chanting together, glorifying Krishna and celebrating the power of the Holy Name. \ud83c\udf38\n\nMusic for Mandir is not just a concert.\nIt is a movement to fill hearts with devotion, spiritual music, and the joy of Krishna Bhakti.\n\nA glimpse from an unforgettable evening in Ahmedabad, where music became a medium for devotion and every chant became a prayer. \ud83e\udd9a\u2728\n\nThe journey continues\u2026\n\n\ud83d\udccd Bangalore \u2014 14 June\n\ud83d\udccd Delhi \u2014 20 June\n\n\ud83c\udf9f\ufe0f Tickets are live now on BookMyShow, District & VCM Website.\n\n#MusicForMandir #MaithiliThakur #MahaMantra #KrishnaBhakti #holyname"},"code":"DZb72_nSCQH","display_uri":"https:\/\/scontent.cdninstagram.com\/v\/t51.71878-15\/721411134_1435491731678683_2485824516250643474_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_s640x640_tt6&_nc_cat=104&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0xJUFMuYmVzdF9pbWFnZV91cmxnZW4uQzMifQ\u00253D\u00253D&_nc_ohc=_OqN0GlSpKEQ7kNvwFuwqAL&_nc_oc=AdpkQILSw_-2-N0dA42Cyq316Ry4RGLc5TDSb1h-oN8FdYHe9VcRdualIfNb_rjlSaYkJ19EUOKAzzU-tkv-t36S&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent.cdninstagram.com&_nc_gid=fcdkUnviKqhXyl67TmBjxA&_nc_ss=78289&oh=00_Af99J4sGzYYNdwikaItFZ9i19itYSLQb1Z9zKJbShjLFIw&oe=6A3304AE","media_type":2,"product_type":"clips","user":{"pk":"1921864800","username":"vcmvrindavan","id":"17841401944000233"},"id":"POLARIS_3916987564829451271"}}]},"id":"17841401944000233","pk":"1921864800","profile_pic_url":"https:\/\/scontent.cdninst